column5:
This is day 1, and ppl are loosing their minds right now.  Think about what I am about to say, this is VERY SERIOUS.

If this is the beginning of a US scare, what do you think ppl are going to do / what will happen when infections without deaths, or at the current statistical low rates, start?  You all who post stuff like this or buy into fear for fears sake, are going to cause PANDAMONIUM.  Please calm the hell down and maybe drink a... Pacifico.  Corona's are piss water.

Killing each other eh?  Current COVID19 media, statics and published material, do not report a high mortality rate.  Right now, at least, the mortality rate is fractional (unconfirmed) at th best or below 3 percent (unlikely), in high rate of infection areas

Where I agree for some concern, people are NOT killing themselves by having a drink, especially when they are using an Uber.  Good on them!

And as it turns out that you choose a weak position to argue from. I'll let you take a guess at which fallacious argument you made.  If you are not sure what I mean by this, wag your finger elsewhere.
I guarantee, some of the boys "dam girl.  Let me come holla atcha!"
Much much worse.  Worst mistake made.

Are y'all f****** serious?  He literally just asked the guy to look into something.  If this wasn't a Presidential candidates running for office, I doubt it would even be an issue.  I asked people to look into BS all the time and I'm not even the president...
What would we do without the social deviance?  So triggered.
I love roe.  Give me some of Dem babies.
Never understood ppls problems with non sexual nudity...
